        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n- May you please explain why tomcat's `logging.properties` is added? What is the effect?\n\n- Does the commit change default logging level from debug to info?\n\n- I suggest spending some time removing the irrelevant diffs in `Dockerfile` and `logback_template.xml. The first seems like no-change besides line-breaks; the latter was reformatted, maybe by Eclipse, so most of the file can be simply \"reverted\".\n\nThanks for you commit!",
        "patchset_number": 1
